org.forgerock.openam.monitoring.cts

Class CtsCRUDOperationsEntryImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.monitoring.cts.CtsCRUDOperationsEntry
      • org.forgerock.openam.monitoring.cts.CtsCRUDOperationsEntryImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, CtsCRUDOperationsEntryMBean

    public class CtsCRUDOperationsEntryImpl
extends CtsCRUDOperationsEntry
    Implementation of the monitoring endpoints for CTS CRUDL operations (query and delete).
    This endpoint should only be used for query(list) and delete operations on the CTS. This is because the token type cannot be determined for these operations. For all other operations use the CtsCRUDOperationsPerTokenTypeEntryImpl.
    Since:
    12.0.0
    See Also:
